net.demilich.metastone.game.spells.custom

Class StoreEntitySpell

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.demilich.metastone.game.spells.Spell
      • net.demilich.metastone.game.spells.custom.StoreEntitySpell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, HasDesc<SpellDesc>

    public class StoreEntitySpell
extends Spell
    Stores the specified SpellArg.TARGET into a list keyed by the source of the casting spell.

    This spell implements Primalfin Champion and Frostmourne.

    Example: 

         {
         "class": "custom.StoreEntitySpell",
         "target": "PENDING_CARD"
     }
    See Also:
    for a spell that retrieves the {@link net.demilich.metastone.game.cards.Card} entities in storage and puts them in your hand., for a {@link net.demilich.metastone.game.spells.desc.source.CardSource} that lets you access the entities stored by this spell., Serialized Form
